19
used in the manufacturing of metals, chemicals, paper, food, and
19
20
beverages, and the purpose of mining, power generation, the
20
21
extraction or washing of minerals or other sources of energy such as
21
22
oil and natural gas; and
22
23
3. “Nonlocal” means a municipality or county that is not within
23
24
the immediate vicinity of a river.
